spec_data.Name: python3-icalendar
spec_data.Description:
Setuptools is a collection of enhancements to the Python 3 distutils that allow
you to more easily build and distribute Python 3 packages, especially ones that
have dependencies on other packages.

This package contains the runtime components of setuptools, necessary to
execute the software that requires pkg_resources.py.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 01:32:12 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Parser/generator of iCalendar files following the RFC 2445 for Python 3
